name: PrudentPanda.co.uk
overview:
PrudentPanda.co.uk is a price comparison website that likes to show the user only what they are looking for - the cheapest prices.

We specialise in home tehnology products such as laptops, tvs and white goods but also include other sectors such as baby products and sports equiment.

PrudentPanda.co.uk includes hundreds of UK retailers and online shopping sites and the price data is updated up to the minute to make sure the users gets the very latest price, delivery and stock information.

We also include any reductions which can be made using voucher codes meaning that we are confident you will not find a product any cheaper at that moment in time. This is why our ‘Comparison of Comparisons’ regularly shows that the prices we find are cheaper than any those shown on other price comparison websites.
